videos.description: TaQuon Marshall throws it deep to Qua Searcy for a 35-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Marshall heaves it up to Searcy for TD

videos.description: Shaun Wilson cuts up field for a 39-yard  gain.
videos.headline: Duke's Wilson breaks free for 39 yards

videos.description: J.J. Green hits the edge for the  3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Green finds the end zone

videos.description: Daniel Jones connects with Shaun Wilson for the 11-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Duke's Jones finds Wilson for TD

videos.description: Duke DL Victor Dimukeje swats the ball and comes up with the interception to spark the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: Duke DL deflects pass for INT

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall finds daylight and runs for a 48-yard pick up.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Marshall jets up field for big gain

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall tucks it and runs for the 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Marshall finds space for TD

videos.description: T.J. Rahming  initially juggles the pass, but recovers for the one-handed grab in traffic.
videos.headline: Duke's Rahming juggles ball and comes up with one-handed catch

videos.description: Brittain Brown leaps over the Georgia Tech defensive line for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Duke's Brown leaps over defenders for TD

videos.description: Daniel Jones finds Shaun Wilson for a 16-yard touchdown to give Duke a 27-20 lead.
videos.headline: Duke's Jones throws short to Wilson for TD

videos.description: Shaun Wilson shows his passing skills with a jump pass to Daniel Helm for the 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Duke's RB Wilson throws jump pass for TD
